             Indicted, for that he, the <rs id="t16781211e-4-cd15" type="crimeDate">25th. of Novem.</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16781211e-4-off16 t16781211e-4-cd15"></join> 1678. did <rs id="t16781211e-4-off16" type="offenceDescription">
